Rating: 4
I'm a seafood lover, and a fisheries biologist, so I'm acutely aware of the impact of fishing on our oceans. That said, I've been looking for recipes that use sustainably caught and farmed seafood. Oysters are great because farming them is actually good for water quality, making them an excellent sustainable choice. Plus, they're farmed close to home. This was an excellent oyster soup - simple, hearty, delicious.

